Great eats for the $!!! 7 delicious wings with a side order of French fries + side of ranch for only $4.99. Where in the hell, are you going to get a better deal then this!? I particularly wanted to try their wings, the rest of the cuban style cafe menu is a delicious given - but these wings were cooked perfectly. They do not add a wing sauce or a favor to your order. Pocket your sauce and come prepared. Otherwise, strip them them down to the bone and eat them like a champ! Their fresh fruit smoothies are sweet to the last drop and a must try! This little Havana Cabana is second to best and a first at serving the breakfast deal in the Cape. The entire family will enjoy an authentic cafeteria style dinning experience here.
